WEBVTT

00:10:00.246 --> 00:10:03.621
Kuchga haqiqatni gapirish qurbonlik 
bo’lmasligi kerak, ammo shunday.

00:10:04.371 --> 00:10:07.537
Agar ko’pchiligimiz buni
yaxshilik uchun tanlagan bo’lsak,

00:10:07.579 --> 00:10:09.871
biz hozirdan ko’ra yaxshiroq 
joyda bo’lamiz.

00:10:11.246 --> 00:10:12.787
Yaxshilik haqida gapirar

00:10:13.454 --> 00:10:16.871
ekanmiz, biz haqiqat ko’priklarinin
o’rnatish uchun haqiqatni gapirishga

00:10:16.871 --> 00:10:18.371
majburmiz deb o’ylayman.

00:10:18.371 --> 00:10:21.621
va haqiqatga asoslanmagan
ko’priklar esa qulaydi.

00:10:21.621 --> 00:10:23.496
Demak, kuch - qudratga gapirish

00:10:23.496 --> 00:10:26.829
bu bizning vazifamiz, bu bizning
majburiyatimiz, bizning burchimiz

00:10:26.871 --> 00:10:29.037
birinchilardan bo’lish, faqat

00:10:29.871 --> 00:10:31.496
qiyin bo’lgan paytlarda emas,